based on following the guide at https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-automate-jenkins-setup-with-docker-and-jenkins-configuration-as-code

see server_ip:8080/configuration-as-code/reference for additional configuration options

USAGE:
update server ip address in casc.yaml (      url: http://128.32.95.154/:8080/)
docker build -t jenkins:jcasc .
docker network create jenkins
docker run --name jenkins --rm --network jenkins --publish 8080:8080 --publish 5000:5000 --env JENKINS_ADMIN_ID=admin --env JENKINS_ADMIN_PASSWORD=password jenkins:jcasc